1. Auth System (Register & Login)

Backend:

/api/auth/register â†’ user create karo

/api/auth/login â†’ token generate karo (JWT)

authMiddleware â†’ protected routes ke liye

Frontend Pages:

Register.jsx â†’ form â†’ API call /api/auth/register

Login.jsx â†’ form â†’ API call /api/auth/login â†’ token Redux store me save

ðŸ‘‰ Start yahin se kyunki bina login/register ke baaki pages ka access nahi milega.

2. User Profile

Backend:

/api/users/me â†’ current user data return (protected route)

/api/users/:id â†’ specific user profile

Frontend Page:

Profile.jsx â†’ API call /api/users/me â†’ profile data show

3. Tournaments

Backend:

/api/tournaments (GET) â†’ all tournaments list

/api/tournaments (POST) â†’ create new tournament (admin only)

/api/tournaments/:id â†’ single tournament details

Frontend Page:

Tournaments.jsx â†’ fetch tournaments list, show cards/table

(Later add: create/join button â†’ POST API call)

4. Matches

Backend:

/api/matches (GET) â†’ list all matches

/api/matches (POST) â†’ create match (admin/organizer)

/api/matches/:id â†’ match details

Frontend Page:

Matches.jsx â†’ show upcoming/past matches

Add "Join Match" logic later

5. Leaderboard

Backend:

/api/leaderboard (GET) â†’ players list sorted by score

Update score when match ends (logic backend me)

Frontend Page:

Leaderboard.jsx â†’ fetch leaderboard data and render table

6. Dashboard/HomePage

Backend: Nahi, ye mainly frontend routing + aggregation page hai

Frontend Page:

Dashboard.jsx â†’ ek layout banega jo Navbar + nested routes (Tournaments, Matches, Leaderboard, Profile) ko hold karega

